<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>app.xmcl.voxelum</id>
  <name>X Minecraft Launcher</name>
  <summary>A modern Minecraft launcher with modpack support</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <developer_name>Voxelum</developer_name>

  <url type="homepage">https://xmcl.app/</url>
  <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com/Voxelum/x-minecraft-launcher/issues</url>
  <url type="help">https://github.com/Voxelum/x-minecraft-launcher/wiki</url>

  <description>
    <p>
    X Minecraft Launcher (XMCL) is a feature-rich Minecraft launcher that lets you manage resources like modpacks, resource packs, mods, and shader packs. It integrates with Minecraft Forge, Fabric, Quilt, CurseForge, and Modrinth.
    </p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-instance management</li>
      <li>Mod installation from CurseForge and Modrinth</li>
      <li>Support for Forge, Fabric, and Quilt mod loaders</li>
      <li>Resource pack and shader pack management</li>
      <li>Multi-account support (Microsoft/Mojang/3rd-party)</li>
      <li>Peer-to-peer multiplayer hosting</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

